When Mark Meadows is to be accused in front of the J6 committee, as they prepare to hold him in contempt of their summons, he has an singular opportunity.

He must walk into the hearing, and ask a lesser committee flunky to allow him to dit down front…

He should reach into his briefcase and withdraw a table placard placing it in front of himself on the table facing the committee.

“Hon. Eric Holder” reads the table tent.

Point of Order, Madam Speaker!

Please desist from referring to me a “Mr. Meadows”

I self-identify as “The Honorable Eric Holder”.

I, and 81,000,000 Trump voters, would appreciate it if you would address me properly, using my full title of identity.
